   512	| `test_token_unique_across_tasks` | Two parallel claims on different tasks produce different tokens. | 04 §3.2 |
   513	| `test_token_unique_across_reclaim_cycles` | Reclaim → re-claim same task → token differs. | 04 §3.2; §5.2 |
   514	| `test_wrong_token_rejected` | Submit with a fabricated token returns 403 `eden://error/wrong-token`. | 04 §3.3 |
