  1102	- Recent plans for prose discipline: [`docs/plans/eden-phase-10e-compose-e2e.md`](eden-phase-10e-compose-e2e.md), [`docs/plans/eden-phase-10d-followup-b-gitea-remote.md`](eden-phase-10d-followup-b-gitea-remote.md).
  1103	
  1104	## Out of scope (reiteration)
  1105	
  1106	This chunk delivers `11a + 11b` exactly. It does NOT deliver:
  1107	
  1108	- **Role-contract scenarios** (per-role submission semantics) → 11c.
  1109	- **Integrator scenarios** (squash shape, eval-manifest shape, work/* discipline) → 11d.
  1110	- **Branch-protection requirement for the `conformance` CI job** → deferred follow-up.
  1111	- **Containerized IUT** (Compose-mode conformance) → either a Phase-10
  1112	  follow-up or chunk 11d's call.
  1113	- **Concurrency / chaos / fault injection** → not in v1.
  1114	- **Non-HTTP wire bindings** → no such binding currently exists in the spec.
  1115	- **Spec amendments other than chapter 09** → if a scenario surfaces
  1116	  spec ambiguity, the fix is a separate spec-amend chunk.
  1117	- **`/v0/`-rooting absence behavior, `X-Eden-Experiment-Id` absence
  1118	  behavior, auth conformance** → not pinned by chapter 07 MUSTs.
  1119	
  1120	## Known risks / things to watch

